    "title": "Architects & Specifiers - Elite South Texas",
    "content": "We are a specialty manufacturer of engineered high performance surfaces & flooring. With over 100 technical support offices worldwide, Elite South Texas is here to help you understand and specify the correct flooring system or surface to meet your client\u2019s specific needs. Our systems are specialty engineered for various applications including interior or exterior surfaces, vertical wall coatings, restoration projects, secondary containment systems and more.\nProduct Divisions\nCSI MasterFormat Code \u2013 Division 09 \u2013 Finishes\n09 67 00 \u2013 Fluid Applied Flooring\n09 67 23 \u2013 Resinous Flooring\n09 67 26 \u2013 Quartz Flooring\n09 96 56 \u2013 Epoxy Coatings\n09 61 13 \u2013 Slip-Resistant Flooring Treatment\n09 62 35 \u2013 Acid-Resistant Flooring\n09 65 36.13 \u2013 Static Dissipative Flooring\n09 96 35 \u2013 Chemical-Resistant Coating\n09 97 26 \u2013 Cementitious Coatings\n09 97 26.13 \u2013 Interior Cementitious Coatings\n09 97 26.23 \u2013 Exterior Cementitious Coatings\nServices We Offer\nOnline AIA courses and in-person Lunch & Learn presentations which earn you a 1-hour CE credit with the AIA\nRon Blank\nContinuing Education Course\nSpecification assistance: including writing of the specification and determining exact system to meet project requirements\nSamples & submittal assistance\nProject site consultations\nVarious consultation resources include phone support, email, online and in-person\nResources & Online Platforms\nDetailed CSI 3-Part MANU-SPECS\u00ae available in the following formats: Microsoft Word, WordPerfect, Spec-Text, MasterSpec or editable PDF.\nAIA Accredited Continuing Education Courses\nRon Blank\nContinuing Education Course\nARCAT\nARCHITIZER\nSWEETS\n4SPECS\nMASTERSPEC\nCONSTRUCTCONNECT\nSPECLINK\nLinkedIn Group\nFacebook Group\nRequest A Sample\nRequest Sample\n\"\n*\n\" indicates required fields\nFirst Name\n*\nLast Name\nLocation\nEmail\n*\nPhone Number\nJob Type\nIndustrial \u2013 Warehouse\nIndustrial \u2013 Aircraft Hangar\nIndustrial \u2013 ESD Flooring\nIndustrial \u2013 Chemical Resistant\nIndustrial \u2013 Other / Not Listed\nGovernment / Public Facilities\nCommercial \u2013 Retail\nCommercial \u2013 Kitchen\nCommercial \u2013 Restaurant\nCommercial \u2013 Hospitality\nCommercial \u2013 Healthcare / Lifestyle\nCommercial \u2013 Office\nCommercial \u2013 Other / Not Listed\nResidential \u2013 Garage Floor\nResidential \u2013 Patio / Sidewalks\nResidential \u2013 Pool Deck\nResidential \u2013 Other / Not Listed\nOther (Please add details in message)\nMessage\nCove Base / Cant Base\nCove Base / Cant Base\nAdditional Documentation\nParamount\nREFLECTOR\nEnhancer HD\nREFLECTOR\nEnhancer",
